        {
            "title": "部分貸款組合承壓 阿波羅私募信貸基金減記資產價值",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 由於部分貸款組合顯現承壓跡象，阿波羅全球管理管理的一只私募信貸基金下調股息並減記資產價值。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">專注於直接貸款的商業發展公司(BDC) MidCap Financial Investment Corp.將季度派息額從每股38美分下調至每股31美分，並將投資組合減記約3%，理由是部分老投資的表現疲軟，以及在利率變動背景下對其長期盈利能力的重新評估。淨投資收益從前一季度的每股38美分小幅升至39美分。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-37bbb461-6109-3b8a-82c0-b8ac915d81f2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"阿波羅全球管理攝影：Jeenah Moon/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LxsQ4KL_CMCq._L8yc8Itw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/80996536a3c3e508973d056293ad4d96\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">阿波羅全球管理攝影：Jeenah Moon/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家BDC正轉向股票回購以提升股東回報，批准了一項新的1億美元股票回購計畫。該股周四收於10.53美元，較該基金季度末每股14.18美元的淨資產價值低約26%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「在目前的交易水平，我們仍認為將資金用於股票回購比投入新投資更能帶來價值，」 MFIC執行長Tanner Powell表示在一份聲明中稱。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著人工智能帶來顛覆性變革，私募信貸管理機構面臨著投資者對其軟件公司投資敞口的擔憂，BDC的業績表現也受到更嚴密審視。由於許多投資組合集中在科技貸款領域，其業績能為日益加劇的估值與信貸壓力提供早期預警。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">首席投資官Ted McNulty在聲明中表示，軟件行業是MFIC投資最集中的行業，截至12月31日，按公允價值計算占投資組合的11.4%，但與其他大多數BDC相比，MFIC對該行業的敞口較小。他還補充說，該基金已做好準備應對人工智能可能帶來的衝擊，重點關注那些擁有成熟、長期客戶關係的企業。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Apollo Private Credit Fund Marks Down Portfolio on Soured Loans</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
